listings.comment: Its best to collaborate with people when building a website. Received copy that had grammar issues etc. I paid for this but still have to work on getting the website ready for publishing

She made a good progress on my website, she created a new design that elevated the atmosphere and experience on my website. One part that amazed me is how she made the custom Add to cart button on my summary on the about us page, giving every page on my website a change to be productive... She's the best!

Alice did an excellent job creating a clear and professional website plan for my farming business. She took the time to understand what I needed and put together a thoughtful plan that fits my goals. I'm really happy with the result and would gladly recommend her work.
She's a great help for my business.

Time spent working with Alice was never a waste. She did amazingly within just a little moment. I am very happy with the outcome of the design and the whole new concept she gave to my website. 
I recommend her for her good works and quality delivery.

A quoted two day project turned into two weeks of little communication and absolutely zero progress. I hired Alice to complete the backend setup of Booqable and integrate it into my website. After enthusiastically encouraging me to accept her quote, that’s when things went quiet. With 2-3 days between responses, each time met with an excuse or just a one line message of little help or updates about the project. After checking myself, I could see that nothing had been touched. I couldn’t possible recommend Alice to anyone if this is the standard of work/communication you can expect. I’m now left feeling extremely disappointed and now my project launch is delayed.
